= SDL_HapticNumEffectsPlaying =
Use this function to return the number of effects a haptic device can play at the same time.


== Syntax ==
```c++
int SDL_HapticNumEffectsPlaying(SDL_Haptic* haptic)
```

== Function Parameters ==
{|
|'''haptic'''
|the haptic device to query ^for^ maximum playing effects
|}

== Return Value ==
Returns the number of effects the haptic device can play at the same time ^or a negative error code on failure^,,, or -1 on error,,; call [[SDL_GetError]]() for more information. <<Color2(green,Should there be a link to Remarks here?)>>

